==Mandarin==
Literally: A true person (of talent) does not show his face.
===Proverb===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' zhēn rén bù lù xiàng or zhēn rén bù lòu xiàng)
# A truly talented individual does not vie for attention by showing off his skills.

